data.description: Being offered with a $5000.00 Seller Concession to help lower that high-interest rate that maybe stopping you from your forever home!!!!!!!!!  Cute and Cozy neighborhood home with a brand new furnace. located on a quiet street with mature shade trees, adorable front and back yard with a sprinkler system, Huge living room windows and brand new sliding door for the back yard.  This cozy home is close to the amenities of Cortez Colorado Stay warm and cool with forced air heat and the a lovely wood burning fireplace, and stay cool with the homes Air Conditioning.   the sellers have just installed a brand new water heater and have taken meticulous care of this charming 3 bed 2 bath home in Cortez.
